# Hero Library Conventions

When generating a hero library using the `@kathrine0/tools:hero-lib` generator, always place it inside the `libs/` directory by passing `--directory`:

```bash
# ✅ CORRECT
npx nx g @kathrine0/tools:hero-lib --name="Wonder Woman" --image="wonder_woman.jpg" --directory="libs/wonder-woman" --no-interactive

# ❌ WRONG - omitting --directory generates the lib in the workspace root
npx nx g @kathrine0/tools:hero-lib --name="Wonder Woman" --image="wonder_woman.jpg" --no-interactive
```
